# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# AVA MC Booking System — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your credentials.
# NEVER commit .env.local or data/payment-configs.json to git.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── App ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXT_PUBLIC_DOMAIN=localhost:3000

# ─── Database ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/ava_mc_booking

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# BankID (Identity / Signing)
# Docs: https://developers.bankid.com/
# Test cert: FPTestcert4_20230629.p12 (passphrase: qwerty123)
# Download: https://developers.bankid.com/getting-started/environments
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
BANKID_ENV=test
# Test:       https://appapi2.test.bankid.com/rp/v6.0
# Production: https://appapi2.bankid.com/rp/v6.0
BANKID_PFX_PATH=./certs/FPTestcert4_20230629.p12
BANKID_PFX_PASSPHRASE=qwerty123

# Also used by Swish and BankID Pay (same test cert):
BANKID_CERT_PATH=./certs/FPTestcert4_20230629.p12
BANKID_CERT_PASSPHRASE=qwerty123

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Roaring.io (Person & Company Data Enrichment)
# Docs: https://developer.roaring.io/
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ROARING_CLIENT_ID=your_sandbox_client_id_here
ROARING_CLIENT_SECRET=your_sandbox_client_secret_here
# ROARING_API_BASE_URL=https://sandbox.roaring.io

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# ██████████████████   FINANCING PROVIDERS   ██████████████████████████████████
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Svea Ekonomi ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs: https://docs.payments.svea.com/docs/
# Apply: https://www.svea.com/se/sv/foretag/betallosningar/
#
# Instore API (Basic Auth)
# Test:       https://webpayinstoreapistage.svea.com
# Production: https://webpayinstoreapi.svea.com
SVEA_INSTORE_USERNAME=your_instore_username_here
SVEA_INSTORE_PASSWORD=your_instore_password_here
# SVEA_INSTORE_API_URL=https://webpayinstoreapistage.svea.com
#
# Checkout + Admin API (HMAC-SHA512)
# Test checkout: https://checkoutapistage.svea.com
# Test admin:    https://paymentadminapistage.svea.com
SVEA_CHECKOUT_MERCHANT_ID=your_merchant_id_here
SVEA_CHECKOUT_SECRET=your_checkout_secret_here
# SVEA_CHECKOUT_API_URL=https://checkoutapistage.svea.com
# SVEA_EXTERNAL_API_URL=https://paymentadminapistage.svea.com
SVEA_MERCHANT_NAME=AVA MC AB

# ─── Santander Consumer Bank Sweden ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:  https://developer.santanderconsumer.se/
# Auth:  Bearer token (API key)
# Note:  Sandbox requires signed merchant agreement — contact open.banking@santanderconsumer.no
SANTANDER_API_KEY=your_santander_api_key_here
SANTANDER_PARTNER_ID=your_santander_partner_id_here
# SANTANDER_API_URL=  ← URL provided by Santander after partner agreement (no public URL)

# ─── Resurs Bank ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:  https://merchant-api.integration.resurs.com/
# Auth:  OAuth2 client_credentials
# Test:  https://merchant-api.integration.resurs.com
# Prod:  Provided at onboarding — contact onboarding@resurs.se
RESURS_CLIENT_ID=your_resurs_client_id_here
RESURS_CLIENT_SECRET=your_resurs_client_secret_here
# RESURS_API_URL=https://merchant-api.integration.resurs.com

# ─── Nordea Finans ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:  https://developer.nordeaopenbanking.com/
# Auth:  OAuth2 authorization-code + QSealC signature
# Test:  https://api.nordeaopenbanking.com
# Note:  Vehicle credit requires a direct Nordea Finans commercial agreement
NORDEA_CLIENT_ID=your_nordea_client_id_here
NORDEA_CLIENT_SECRET=your_nordea_client_secret_here
# NORDEA_API_URL=https://api.nordeaopenbanking.com  ← Open Banking confirmed; vehicle credit URL provided by Nordea Finans

# ─── Ikano Bank ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:  https://www.ikanobank.se/foretag/
# Auth:  X-Api-Key header
# Note:  Merchant POS financing requires a direct commercial agreement with Ikano
IKANO_API_KEY=your_ikano_api_key_here
IKANO_STORE_ID=your_ikano_store_id_here
# IKANO_API_URL=  ← URL provided by Ikano after partner agreement (https://api.ikanobank.se unverified for merchant API)

# ─── Walley (f.d. Collector Bank) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:  https://dev.walleypay.com/docs/checkout/
# Auth:  OAuth2 client_credentials (WALLEY_STORE_ID = client_id, WALLEY_SHARED_KEY = client_secret)
# Test:  https://api.uat.walleydev.com  (UAT scope: 705798e0-8cef-427c-ae00-6023deba29af/.default)
# Prod:  https://api.walleypay.com       (Prod scope: a3f3019f-2be9-41cc-a254-7bb347238e89/.default)
# Manage credentials in Merchant Hub: https://merchanthub.aks.uat.walleydev.com
WALLEY_STORE_ID=your_walley_client_id_here
WALLEY_SHARED_KEY=your_walley_client_secret_here
# WALLEY_API_URL=https://api.uat.walleydev.com

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# ██████████████████   BNPL PROVIDERS   ███████████████████████████████████████
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Klarna ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:  https://docs.klarna.com/
# Auth:  HTTP Basic Auth (username:password)
# Test:  https://api.playground.klarna.com
# Prod:  https://api.klarna.com
KLARNA_API_URL=https://api.playground.klarna.com
KLARNA_API_USERNAME=your_klarna_api_username_here
KLARNA_API_PASSWORD=your_klarna_api_password_here

# ─── Qliro ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:  https://developers.qliro.com/
# Auth:  MerchantApiKey field in request body (NOT a header)
# Test:  https://pago.qit.nu
# Test personal numbers: 790625-5307 (approved), 770530-1773 (on hold), 750420-8104 (denied)
QLIRO_API_KEY=your_qliro_api_key_here
QLIRO_MERCHANT_ID=your_qliro_merchant_id_here
# QLIRO_API_URL=https://pago.qit.nu        ← test (confirmed). Production URL provided by Qliro at onboarding

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# ██████████████████   INSTANT / DIREKTBETALNING   ████████████████████████████
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Swish ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:  https://developer.swish.nu/
# Auth:  Mutual TLS (mTLS) — same test cert as BankID (FPTestcert4_20230629.p12)
# Test (MSS simulator): https://mss.cpc.getswish.net/swish-cpcapi/api/v2/
# Production:           https://cpc.getswish.net/swish-cpcapi/api/v2/
# NOTE: CA chain changed 2025-03-20 → GeoTrust TLS RSA CA G1 / DigiCert Global Root G2
SWISH_PAYEE_ALIAS=1231181189
SWISH_CERT_PATH=./certs/FPTestcert4_20230629.p12
SWISH_CERT_PASSPHRASE=qwerty123
# SWISH_API_URL=https://mss.cpc.getswish.net/swish-cpcapi/api/v2

# ─── Trustly ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:  https://docs.trustly.com/
# Auth:  JSON-RPC 1.1 + RSA-2048 signature (NOT OAuth2/Bearer)
# Test:  https://test.trustly.com/api/1
# Prod:  https://api.trustly.com
# Back office (test): https://test.trustly.com/backoffice
# TRUSTLY_PRIVATE_KEY is the PEM-encoded RSA private key for signing requests
TRUSTLY_API_KEY=your_trustly_processing_account_username
TRUSTLY_MERCHANT_ID=your_trustly_merchant_id_here
TRUSTLY_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN RSA PRIVATE KEY-----\nyour_private_key_here\n-----END RSA PRIVATE KEY-----"
# TRUSTLY_API_URL=https://test.trustly.com/api/1  ← test. Production: https://api.trustly.com/1  (note: /1 not /api/1)

# ─── BankID Pay ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:  https://developers.bankid.com/
# Auth:  Mutual TLS — same RP certificate as BankID signing
# Test:  https://appapi2.test.bankid.com/rp/v6.0
# Production: https://appapi2.bankid.com/rp/v6.0
# ⚠️  API v5.x was discontinued Sep 2024 — only v6.0 is supported
# ⚠️  personalNumber is no longer accepted — use QR code or autoStartToken
BANKID_PAY_CLIENT_ID=your_bankid_pay_client_id
BANKID_PAY_CLIENT_SECRET=your_bankid_pay_client_secret
# BANKID_API_URL=https://appapi2.test.bankid.com/rp/v6.0

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# ██████████████████   CARD TERMINAL (Blipp / Chip+PIN)   █████████████████████
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Nets Easy / AXEPT Terminal ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:   https://developer.nexigroup.com/nets-easy/en-EU/api/payment-v1/
# Auth:   Secret key in Authorization header — NO "Bearer" prefix
# Test:   https://test.api.dibspayment.eu
# Prod:   https://api.dibspayment.eu
# Portal: https://portal.dibspayment.eu/registration
# Keys in portal: Company > Integration (secretKey + checkoutKey)
NETS_API_KEY=your_nets_secret_key_here
NETS_MERCHANT_ID=your_nets_merchant_id_here
NETS_TERMINAL_ID=your_nets_axept_terminal_id_here
NETS_CHECKOUT_KEY=your_nets_checkout_key_here
# NETS_API_URL=https://test.api.dibspayment.eu

# ─── Adyen Terminal ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:   https://docs.adyen.com/point-of-sale/
# Auth:   X-API-Key header
# Test management: https://management-test.adyen.com/v3
# Test checkout:   https://checkout-test.adyen.com/v71
# Terminal cloud:  https://terminal-api-test.adyen.com/sync
# Generate API key: Customer Area → Developers → API credentials → Authentication
ADYEN_API_KEY=your_adyen_api_key_here
ADYEN_MERCHANT_ACCOUNT=your_adyen_merchant_account_here
ADYEN_CLIENT_KEY=your_adyen_client_key_here
ADYEN_TERMINAL_ID=your_adyen_terminal_serial_here
# ADYEN_MANAGEMENT_URL=https://management-test.adyen.com/v3
# ADYEN_CHECKOUT_URL=https://checkout-test.adyen.com/v71

# ─── Stripe Terminal ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:   https://stripe.com/docs/terminal
# Auth:   Bearer sk_test_… (test) / sk_live_… (production)
# URL:    https://api.stripe.com/v1/ (same for test and production — key prefix determines mode)
# Note:   STRIPE_SECRET_KEY is shared between Stripe online and Stripe Terminal
STRIPE_LOCATION_ID=tml_loc_your_location_id_here

# ─── Bambora Terminal ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:   https://developer.bambora.com/
# Auth:   Login token via https://login-v1.api-eu.bambora.com
# Note:   BAMBORA_API_KEY and BAMBORA_MERCHANT_ID are shared with Bambora Online
# Same credentials — no separate terminal env vars needed

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# ██████████████████   CARD ONLINE   ██████████████████████████████████████████
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Stripe Online ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:   https://stripe.com/docs/api
# Auth:   Bearer token — key prefix determines test vs live mode
# URL:    https://api.stripe.com/v1/ (same endpoint always)
# Test keys start with sk_test_ / pk_test_
# Live keys start with sk_live_ / pk_live_
# Get keys: Stripe Dashboard → Developers → API keys
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_your_stripe_secret_key_here
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_your_stripe_publishable_key_here
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_your_stripe_webhook_secret_here

# ─── Adyen Online ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Uses same ADYEN_API_KEY, ADYEN_MERCHANT_ACCOUNT, ADYEN_CLIENT_KEY as Adyen Terminal above
# No additional env vars needed for online payments

# ─── Bambora Online ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs:   https://developer.bambora.com/europe
# Auth:   Login token via https://login-v1.api-eu.bambora.com  (format: {merchantId}@{apiKey})
# Services: Checkout (api.v1.checkout.bambora.com), Transaction (transaction-v1.api-eu.bambora.com)
# Note:   Same credentials for online and terminal
BAMBORA_API_KEY=your_bambora_api_key_here
BAMBORA_MERCHANT_ID=your_bambora_merchant_number_here

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# ██████████████████   BANK TRANSFER   ████████████████████████████████████████
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Banköverföring ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# No external API — customer makes a manual bank transfer using an OCR reference.
# OCR references are auto-generated using Luhn mod-10 (Bankgirot standard).
# Format: Bankgiro XXX-XXXX (7 digits), IBAN SE + 22 digits
BANKGIRO_NUMBER=123-4567
BANK_ACCOUNT_IBAN=SE4550000000058398257466
